        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "（闹钟声）…………",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "啊呀！糟了，什么破东西！本小姐明明记得已经关掉了才对……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "芬妮？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "里芙无限之视",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "也睡了够久了，是该叫他起来了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "里芙……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "哎呀，办公楼那边的人不来催，咱们自己急什么嘛……哎？亲爱的，你别醒！你接着睡回去！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "还没来得及睁开的眼睛被她用手轻轻捂住，然后我就感觉到自己胸口一沉，一股香风飘进了我的鼻息里。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……我睡了多久？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "里芙无限之视",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "十几个小时吧。怎么样，还觉得累吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她应该是正坐在床边，我能感觉到她在用手帮我整理着被角。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "好多了。她们俩还好吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "都没什么问题，别担心！补了营养液，做了全身的检查，然后就都送回房间了，现在应该也还在睡觉呢。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "床榻一阵颤动，她从我身上翻到了一旁，侧躺在了我身边，原本捂住我眼睛的手在我的脸颊上滑动着。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我说啊，家里的男主人，你行行好嘛，别那么拼命啦！你知不知道我昨天忙完了回来，她们说你们三个还在那个什么“纺锤”系统里……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我和星期三跑到监测终端那边去一看，三个人，满屏的指数，没一个是正常的！你是不是想吓死谁呀……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "哎呀我跟你说话呐——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "b-1",
        "Flag": "b-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "b-1-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "回应芬妮的爱意",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "比起开口，此刻我有着更合适的方式去回应她的关切——我晃了晃脑袋，把半张脸向着她的方向凑了过去。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "里芙无限之视",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "噗嗬……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "哼……最会得了便宜卖乖啦！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 2,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "用双唇在我的脸上印出一片湿痕，她终于肯消了气，而我也彻底摆脱了困意，睁开了眼睛。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "里芙无限之视",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "要起来吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嗯，没事，手脚都还在，健全着呢！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "用力伸一个懒腰，然后在她们俩都没察觉的情况下一把将她们都搂进怀里，在惊叫和笑声中，我离开了温软的床铺。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "里芙无限之视",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "陶董和辰星她们应该在等你，情报分析部门那边三班倒，把目前能掌握的都调查的差不多了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "所以，我的达令……你觉得这次会是谁？罗赞那个疯婆子，还是舍塔那个老妖怪？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嗯……都有可能，不过是谁不重要。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那什么重要？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "手法。对眼下的咱们来说，到底是怎么做到的比到底是谁做的更要紧一些。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "真神者势力抬头以后，不光是我们，所有有能力将泰坦物质视为一种资源的势力都会换一个眼光来看待现在的局势。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "对方这一次这么神乎其技，而且是在半年以前就已经掌握了这种程度的运用水平……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 33,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "里芙无限之视",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "先别想那么多了，见招拆招就好。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 34,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她轻抚着我的脊背，温柔地凝望着我，目光中有着足以让我安心的力量。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "就是！一家之主嘛，打起精神来！每天想那么多啊……眉毛都拧一块儿去了！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "芬妮从我身后绕过来，仔细地帮我整理着衣领。过了好一会儿，她后退了小半步，睁大了眼睛上上下下把我打量了个仔细，然后才露出了满意的笑容。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "好啦，这样就没问题啦！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 38,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你们两个手头的事情都还顺利吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 39,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "里芙无限之视",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嗯……按部就班吧，有进展，但不快。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 40,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "联合训练的事情交给本小姐，新战术套装的适应性改良有星期三帮你盯着，别太担心我们俩，都好着呢！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 41,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "好。那……晚上见。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 42,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "里芙无限之视",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "啊……嗯，晚上见。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 43,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 4,
        "Speaker": "芬妮辉耀",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "可要精神饱满地回来哦！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 44,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在挚爱之人的脸上留下粉红的云雾之后，我走出了房门。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 45,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "总部的走廊里一如既往地安静，但我心里清楚，一墙之隔，几乎所有的部门此刻都在紧锣密鼓地忙碌着。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 46,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "世界树需要面对的状况越来越复杂，敌人的数量和手段也在不断增多。甜蜜的生活和严苛的任务，两者我都要仔细品尝才行。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 47,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卡罗琳",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "啊……我以为你还睡着呢，还想晚点再去叫你来着。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 48,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在陶办公室的门口，我撞见了正抱着一摞文件，脚步匆匆的卡罗琳。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 49,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这都是什么啊？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 50,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卡罗琳",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "唉……协助调查北庭卫的通告函，还有这个，公司股权再分配的新闻通稿，这个是一会儿要给霍尔姆出入境管理处送过去的盖章文件，啊——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 51,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她一边数着手里文件的份数，一边机械地向我说明着。但怀里抱着的东西实在太多，一个不小心将其中一份掉在了地上。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 52,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卡罗琳",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我自己来就行了分析员，你快进去吧，陶董和辰星等着呢……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 53,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我弯下腰，帮着她把掉落的那一份捡了起来。薄薄的几页纸，中间夹着一张由世界树财务部签发的票据。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 54,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卡罗琳",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "呃，这个……是给卜卜家里人的，她老家不在这边，我们得用纸质的……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 55,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "去吧去吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 56,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卡罗琳",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "哎，好。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 57,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "慰劳津贴……一个已经很久很久没在我脑子里出现过的名词就这么突然地蹦到我眼前。我强压着内心翻涌的情绪，推开门走进了陶的办公室。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 58,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 59,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "陶",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "身体怎么样了？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 60,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "没什么大碍，咱们直奔主题吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 61,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "您之前让我去查的事情有一点点进展了，姬家之前在北庭卫的那处祖产，确实是一处矿产。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 62,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "差不多半个世纪以前，那处产业一夜之间遭到废弃，所有相关的资料，知情人，各种信息全部都被人为地销毁或隐藏了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 63,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "舍塔。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 64,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嗯，顺着这个思路想的话，她一定脱不了干系。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 65,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我现在还在努力打探，看看能不能从一些黑市的情报商人手里买到一些有用的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 66,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "家里人……老一辈的，有愿意开口的吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 67,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "呵，这是另一桩怪事了。我现在……联系不到家里那边了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 68,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "联系不到？他们不是之前还专门派人送家书过来吗……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 69,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "辰星",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嗯，当时我为了搞清楚那封家书是怎么回事，不就试过联系他们吗，那个时候就没人应。现在也一样。不知道家里人在搞什么。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 70,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "陶",
