    },
    {
        "Key": 138,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我无声地向她比着手势，换来的是她更加爽朗的笑容。随后，我迈向了通往宿舍天台的楼梯。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 139,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "日光煦暖，天台空荡，只有她一个人躺在竹椅上，两条腿伸得直直的，白得直发光。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 140,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "肴病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嘿……我刚刚还在想，你到底什么时候会找到这儿来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 141,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你……知道我正找你呢？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 142,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "肴病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "啊……不知道，我什么都不知道。不过你来了正好，给——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 143,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她打了个大大的哈欠，顺手把一瓶防晒霜扔了过来，然后整个人就翻了个身，舒舒服服地趴在了躺椅上。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 144,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "肴病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "芙提雅还好吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 145,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "说是睡回笼觉呢，我也还没见着。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 146,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "肴病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嗯……是都该歇一歇了……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 147,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你呢？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 148,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "肴病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我？我好着呢。哎，上边，对……右边一点！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 149,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "午后的阳光照在我的脸上，照在她的身上。我不紧不慢地帮她涂着防晒霜，两个人有一搭没一搭地聊着……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 150,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "有那么一瞬间，我的神情有些恍惚，好像这样的场景曾经无数次地发生过，好像整个海姆达尔部队生来就该像这样悠闲地在一起生活。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 151,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "肴病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "哎？走神儿啦？问你呐……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 152,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "啊？什么？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 153,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "肴病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我说，在你眼里，我现在是个什么样儿啊？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 154,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "没有什么现在过去和以后，你在我眼里一直都是一个样。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 155,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "肴病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "哈……好啊，那你告诉我嘛，是什么样？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 156,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "好看的样子。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 157,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "肴病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我可是很认真地在问你呢。",
